  "ciliary_role": "Recruited by ARL13B and FIP5 (30120249). Higher activity initiating glutamate chains than elongating them. Required for RPGRORF15 function as it seems to be highly selective (27162334). Essential for the correct function of sperm flagella. It might also be responsible for the tubulin polyglutami tion in the microtubule triplets of the centrioles, increasing the centriole stability. Mutations have been identified as cause of recessive reti l dystrophy (24791901), and reduced sperm motility and infertility in humans (28173158).",
